Zuma Says Ruling ANC May Probe Fraudently Appointed Candidates in Election

-- B y   F r a n z   W i l d
-- 
2011-04-28T07:57:09Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-28/zuma-says-ruling-anc-may-probe-fraudently-appointed-candidates-in-election.html
Jacob Zuma , president of  South
Africa ’s ruling  African National Congress , said the party will
investigate fraudulently appointed candidates for local
government elections on May 18.  The ANC will remove candidates not preferred by party
structures, Zuma, who is also South Africa’s president, told
reporters at the ANC’s headquarters in Johannesburg today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Franz Wild in Johannesburg at 
 fwild@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Vernon Wessels at 
 vwessels@bloomberg.net  